We have many skillful characters at our disposal who may be deployed on missions in order to sway campaign conditions to the favor of the Empire.  Each character has a unique set of abilities which make him or her more or less capable of succeeding at certain missions.  To examine a character's abilities, right-click on that character and select 'Status' from the menu.  The character's values in Diplomacy, Espionage, Combat, and Leadership, among other items, will be visible in the Status Window.  Many missions, such as Espionage or Diplomacy require skills in these areas; the higher a character's values are in a particular category, the more likely it is that they will succeed on a mission requiring that skill.  Research missions, however, require more specialized abilities; you can discover whether a character is capable of such missions by examining the `R&D' section of their status window.